{"tid":551121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電熱水爐】小學女生衣衫單薄　報稱被迫熱水不足下洗澡　警拘父母","createTime":"2018-02-05T11:00:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T09:59:18.000Z","uid":11001,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"35954e30eb04ce0c06d747ef48680e471d272833","tid":551121,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"黃大仙發生虐兒案。一名11歲女學生，今天被學校社工發現，未有穿上足夠禦寒衣物保暖。消息稱，近日天氣寒冷，惟女生仍被迫在家中電熱水爐熱水不足下洗澡；另社工及校方上周已發現女生衣衫單薄，至今天見問題未有改善後，決定報警。警方經調查後，拘捕其父母。<br />\n<br />\n現場為獻主會溥仁小學，校方職員回覆《明報》查詢時表示，案件已交由警方跟進，不便回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00001/1517825648797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00001%2F1517825648797&d=n4WfTD7JfggnSmlMA93jA8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9b531a76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00001%2F1517825648797&h=7fbd8d9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00001/1517825648797</a>"},{"pid":"c63a00e5401c42d4de66ca372b453a32f29cd9d0","tid":551121,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"捉佢父母打靶"},{"pid":"61e75114a87b67400d071763f2d6c3afb6e7db14","tid":551121,"uid":38671,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"儲水式熱水爐根本只適合無冬天既國家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91efedb2ce3b0e95d691f4b6197eb3c66b9a55e","tid":551121,"uid":2429,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"要求禁售儲水式電熱水爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfe32b147fbf5234f21d68bd89d0d0b17b6797a","tid":551121,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T11:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},